race.description: Sires On Ice (Wa) Young Stars Classic Final
race.comment: STARLIGHT SNOWY (1) is on a hot streak of form, jumping from this box to score last time at this track (30.48), making it three straight wins. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. DIVOT (2) has a strong winning strike-rate here with two wins and a placing from four tries. Scored by 7 lengths last time (29.86) in a OPEN over 520m at this track. Can feature with the right run. JUST A PIASTRI (8) is progressing well claiming his 3rd career win latest, scoring by 9 lengths (29.77) at this track. Likely to be in the finish. WEST ON MODEL (3) put a gap on her rivals last start. Must be respected.
